{"tid":1390920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"運動的終局近了","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:23:36.000Z","uid":129990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1da7c7acdd4488d649d1a98a72f0e64c2b5b960d","tid":1390920,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"呢場運動就黎收皮，義士被捕入獄，個班離地中產就繼續生活，香港繼續被赤化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔得！唔得！屌你老母！唔好依個時候先黎輸</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港已經冇撚得再輸！今次唔成功爭取到民主既話，我地就會滅亡，公民社會從此一沉百踩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n83旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n84將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n85全港大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次佔領既時候講諗下當日既「勇武行動」係想達到咩目的？<br />\n想讓前線警員受壓？<br />\n想以佔領阻礙市民生活而對政權施壓？<br />\n定係無原因純粹為佔而佔？<br />\n<br />\n唔係想批評前線，但係每次咁樣損兵折將，前線總有一日會收哂皮，你估香港真係有好多「勇武派」？達成左目的，就be water走人，咁先可以保留實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，請諗清楚黎緊點做好？<br />\n如果要「光復香港，時代革命」，就玩大d, 真真正正既革命，直至有民主選舉為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要「五大訴求，缺一不可」，就請思考好每次「勇武行動」真正目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好由「勇武派」變做「送頭派」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6294e892bd19ae8459117b279eb107a044e69d","tid":1390920,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KemKtXu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKemKtXu.png&h=a472b3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2F7rJ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2F7rJ9.png&h=a5a67f40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tomynhv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTomynhv.png&h=4e3f79d3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}